lization of gene-inactivating mutations are available at our UCSC genome browser mirror https://genome.senckenberg.de.</p></sec><supplementary-material><ext-link xlink:href="elife-77999-supp-v1.zip">Download zip</ext-link><p>Any figures and tables for this article are included in the PDF. The zip folder contains additional supplemental files.</p></supplementary-material></sec></back></article>